# BabyGPT

This repository is **BabyGPT**, a ChatGPT-style Next.js app. It is **not** PostForge.

## Product rules

- Single page route: `/` plus API routes under `/api/*`.
- No Prisma, Stripe, server auth sessions, or databases. Community posts are in-memory on the server process.
- Client persistence uses `localStorage` only, with keys prefixed `babygpt_`.
- Call `z-ai-web-dev-sdk` **only** in Route Handlers / server code — never import it in client components.

## Configuration

- Set `Z_AI_BASE_URL` and `Z_AI_API_KEY` in `.env.local` for local development.

## Verification

- Title: "BabyGPT — AI Chat Assistant"
- Dark UI, robot logo, quantum controls, community panel, streaming chat when API keys are valid.
